Join Dijets Inc. tech & innovation programme, to learn more about web3 and how Dijets is building the next generation of the internet?: Dijets 'The New Internet' campaign, explores what the next evolution of the internet will mean for our society and economy, and the role Dijets Inc. aims to play in building this.

Web 3.0 is decentralized, meaning that and individual can own their online identity, become an active stakeholder in the internet, and be free to move their data outside of the confines of a single platform. However, this evolution - and the opportunities from both an individual and business perspective that it may bring - reveals critical questions that need to be addressed by both the creators and end users as we seek to develop a fairer internet. Web 3.0 often refers to the principles that will guide the evolution of the internet and the emerging technologies that will underpin it.

This is an opportunity to develop your understanding of web3 and Dijets Inc's strategy to , and begin to navigate how different parts of the tech sector will play a role in bridging web 2.0 and 3.0 together
